title: 14 Celebs Posing Awkwardly With Teeth Whiteners The Cut
text:
Photo: khloekardashian/Instagram
Celebrities take their dental health extremely seriously. So seriously, in fact, that many of them have begun posting ads on their Instagram accounts for an on-the-go teeth-whitening system from Express Smile Atlanta , a "professional teeth whitening business." Suddenly everybody from Khloé Kardashian to Lea Michele is holding a small plastic device up to their faces and illuminating their grins in creepy blue light.
Behold, 14 celebrities attempting to look cute while shilling for teeth whitening.
Love how quick #ExpressSmileAtlanta works! It makes me smile! Use code #LEA for $15 off! http://t.co/C8M2fyGWv8 #ad pic.twitter.com/utNqK18uyo
— Lea Michele (@msleamichele) July 30, 2015
